  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">PACT 3 Training Montenegro</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="SK">PACT 3 &#x161;kolenie v &#x10C;iernej Hore</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="SK">&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Projekt si kladie za cie&#x13E; podpori&#x165; vl&#xE1;du &#x10C;iernej Hory v prechode na akru&#xE1;lne &#xFA;&#x10D;tovn&#xED;ctvo a prijatie Medzin&#xE1;rodn&#xFD;ch &#xFA;&#x10D;tovn&#xFD;ch &#x161;tandardov pre verejn&#xFD; sektor (IPSAS).&#xA0;Certifikovan&#xE9; &#x161;kolenie pre &#xFA;&#x10D;tovn&#xED;kov verejn&#xE9;ho sektora (PACT)&#xA0;prispieva k zv&#xFD;&#x161;enej transparentnosti a lep&#x161;iemu riadeniu verejn&#xFD;ch financi&#xED; (PFM) v &#x10C;iernej Hore, v s&#xFA;lade s Programom reformy PFM na roky 2016-2020.&#xA0;V obdob&#xED; od jesene 2018 do jari 2020 bude v &#x10C;iernej Hore program PACT pokra&#x10D;ova&#x165; &#x161;kolen&#xED;m tretej gener&#xE1;cie (G3), prostredn&#xED;ctvom ktor&#xE9;ho bude vy&#x161;kolen&#xFD;ch do 40 &#x161;tudentov na &#xFA;rovni certifik&#xE1;tu. Bude obsahova&#x165; tri &#x161;koliace moduly a lokaliza&#x10D;n&#xFA; podporu, ktor&#xE9; doplnia peer-to-peer vzdel&#xE1;vacie podujatia.&lt;/p&gt;</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">&lt;p&gt;The project aims at supporting the Government of Montenegro in transition towards accrual accounting and adoption of the International Public Sector Accounting Standards (IPSAS). The Public Accountants Certification Training (PACT) contributes to increased public financial management (PFM) accountability, transparency and performance of Montenegro, in line with the PFM Reform Program for 2016-2020.&#xA0;In the period between autumn 2018 and spring 2020, the PACT program will continue in Montenegro through training a third generation (G3) of up to 40 students at the certificate level. It will entail three training modules and localization support that will be complemented with peer learning events.&lt;/p&gt;</narrative>
  </description>
